import { useEffect, useContext, useState, useRef } from "react"; import TopNav from "../../topNav/js/topNav"; import "../css/longs.css"; import uryFirstVideo from "../../../videos/uryFirstVideo.mp4"; import { UseContextValues } from "../../../App"; export default function LongsComp() { const videoInfo = useContext(UseContextValues); const [uryFirstVideo, setUryFirstVideo] = useState({}); const [urySecondVideo, setUrySecondVideo] = useState({}); const [urySubs, setUrySubs] = useState({}); const [beterVideo, setBeterVideo] = useState({}); const [beterSubs, setBeterSubs] = useState({}); const middleElement = useRef(null); useEffect(() => { console.log(videoInfo); setUryFirstVideo(videoInfo.uryFirstVideo); setUrySecondVideo(videoInfo.urySecondVideo); setUrySubs(videoInfo.urySubs); setBeterVideo(videoInfo.beterVideo); setBeterSubs(videoInfo.beterSubs); }, [videoInfo.fetchingResult]); function activeSelectedVideo(e) { Array.from(middleElement.current.children).forEach((ele) => { ele.children[1].style.cssText = ""; ele.children[1].children[0].style.cssText = ""; ele.children[1].children[1].style.cssText = ""; }); e.currentTarget.children[1].style.cssText = "border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color); width: 100%; height: 100%; transition: 0.2s;"; e.currentTarget.children[1].children[0].style.cssText = "padding: 28px 10px 0px 0px;"; e.currentTarget.children[1].children[1].style.cssText = "transform: translateX(33px);"; } return (
{urySecondVideo.views}
{urySecondVideo.likes}
{urySubs.subscribers} subscribers
